\subsection{Calculus in $\RR 3$}
We will prove the following identities (see the summary %\ref{â€¢}, for 
details):
\begin{eqnarray*}
    d\,f &= [\mathtt{grad}\,f]_1 \\
    d\,[T]_1 &= [\mathtt{curl}\,T]_2 \\
    d\,[T]_2 &= [\mathtt{div}\,T]_3
\end{eqnarray*}
